WEBVTT

00:00.360 --> 00:01.760
   Previously on St Elsewhere -

00:01.760 --> 00:04.120
Sometimes Ehrlich doesn't
    have any sense.

00:04.120 --> 00:05.600
Drop him from my rotation.

00:05.600 --> 00:06.640
&lt; My sister, Morena.

00:06.640 --> 00:10.600
She doesn't speak much English.
Just got here from El Salvador.

00:10.600 --> 00:13.120
The board has adopted
only two of the proposals,

00:13.120 --> 00:14.840
and haven't put either
      into action.

00:14.840 --> 00:17.920
       I'm transferring you to OBGYN.

00:17.920 --> 00:19.400
I'll apologise immediately.
This will never happen again.

00:19.400 --> 00:22.080
I'll apologise immediately.
This will never happen again.
    You start tomorrow morning.

