 in here -

00:24.240 --> 00:26.760
one rotten marriage
after another,

00:26.760 --> 00:30.760
and those bratty kids
of yours... Ow!

02:14.520 --> 02:15.400
You want a drink?

02:15.400 --> 02:19.400
You want a drink?
No, thanks! Go on!

02:27.840 --> 02:30.520
           Bob... Bob...

02:30.520 --> 02:31.640
Beat it, Ehrlich.

02:31.640 --> 02:32.680
        This is important.

02:32.680 --> 02:34.320
I'm the last guy you wanna talk to.

02:34.320 --> 02:36.600
I stepped over the line
on the Boynton case,

02:36.600 --> 02:38.280
 scared a patient out of surgery,

02:38.280 --> 02:41.480
but did you have to tell Craig
to kick me out of the department?

02:41.480 --> 02:45.280
That was his idea.
I wanted to tear your head off.

02:45.280 --> 02:47.640
 Look, medicine's a judgment call.

02:47.640 --> 02:49.160
    I tried using my judgment.

02:49.160 --> 02:51.000
Yeah, that was your first mistake.

02:51.000 --> 02:52.680
 I'm sorry, OK? I'll do anything.

02:52.680 --> 02:56.440
I'll never take another plastics
rotation, I'll handle the burn ward.

02:56.440 --> 02:58.080
 Just get me back in the surgery.

02:58.080 --> 03:00.240
I gave you more chances
     than you deserve.

03:00.240 --> 03:01.840
Got sandbagged for it.

03:01.840 --> 03:05.280
You don't understand, OK?
You wanna hate me, that's just fine,

03:05.280 --> 03:08.200
but I've got to prove myself
to Craig otherwise he'll drop me

03:08.200 --> 03:10.960
from the residency programme.
Then where would I be?

03:10.960 --> 03:14.960
Ehrlich, I don't care if you end up
in a taxidermy shop stuffing tuna.

03:15.160 --> 03:16.480
     Which brings us to OBGYN.

03:16.480 --> 03:19.960
Craig transferred me there so I
could learn interpersonal skills.

03:19.960 --> 03:21.840
Obviously I need work in that area.

03:21.840 --> 03:24.680
Dealing with women
isn't my long suit, you know?

03:24.680 --> 03:28.680
Kicked out of surgery, out of OBGYN,
next stop's the street corner.

03:28.920 --> 03:32.800
You know something? I don't give
a rat's can about your problems.

03:32.800 --> 03:35.280
You're one of those
high-school lightweights

03:35.280 --> 03:37.360
who ran to teacher
              when things got rough.

03:37.360 --> 03:40.320
What? This is because
I was lousy at dodgeball?!

03:40.320 --> 03:44.320
Stay out of my way.

03:48.440 --> 03:52.440
Come on, son. Finish up, there.

03:55.200 --> 03:56.400
Buenas dias, Morena. &gt;

03:56.400 --> 03:57.440
Hello.

03:57.440 --> 03:57.880
Hi, Dad.

03:57.880 --> 03:59.280
Hi, Dad.
&lt; Hi.

03:59.280 --> 04:02.080
I called a taxi for you.
They'll pick you up in an hour.

04:02.080 --> 04:06.080
An hour? I've only got
        a million things left to do.

04:07.200 --> 04:10.520
OK. Come on, son. Time to get
you to school. Get your coat.

04:10.520 --> 04:12.080
Tommy stay Morena.

04:12.080 --> 04:16.079
&lt; No, you're going to school.

04:16.240 --> 04:18.160
Morena, thanks for doing my laundry.

04:18.160 --> 04:20.200
Yes.

04:20.200 --> 04:23.200
You know, she's only been here
      a week and already she knows

04:23.200 --> 04:25.680
how to run the house.
I really like her.

04:25.680 --> 04:28.240
She makes the strongest coffee
in the world.

04:28.240 --> 04:32.240
Tommy hasn't gotten along with
anyone this well since Mrs Catalano.

04:32.320 --> 04:33.360
He's gonna be late.

04:33.360 --> 04:37.120
I'll get him.

04:37.120 --> 04:40.800
Oh, Dad? I'm gonna need
some more money for school.

04:40.800 --> 04:44.800
I just sent you a cheque last week.

05:18.280 --> 05:22.280
Tommy! Tommy, come here!

05:23.720 --> 05:26.880
  Morena, if the plumber calls...

05:26.880 --> 05:28.960
Plumber?

05:28.960 --> 05:30.160
                          Never mind.

05:30.160 --> 05:34.160
Dad! Come up here, quick! &gt;

05:35.280 --> 05:36.920
Tommy, come here!

05:36.920 --> 05:40.920
&lt; Tommy!

05:40.960 --> 05:42.280
              Lizzie?

05:42.280 --> 05:45.320
Dad, he climbed out! &gt;

05:45.320 --> 05:47.160
    Tommy!

05:47.160 --> 05:50.400
&lt; Tommy!

05:50.400 --> 05:53.760
         Tommy, come here!

05:53.760 --> 05:55.560
Thomas!

