the admitting list. I'm sorry.

06:38.200 --> 06:41.000
Well, are you sure
you brought your wife here?

06:41.000 --> 06:43.120
Well, our hospital
is made out of brick.

06:43.120 --> 06:45.920
What did the place you took
your wife look like?

06:45.920 --> 06:48.400
 Oh, no, no. That's St Cecilia's.

06:48.400 --> 06:51.040
St Cecilia's has a fountain
outside. What?

06:51.040 --> 06:53.560
I know. Yeah, I'm sure
it's a very good hospital.

06:53.560 --> 06:55.760
          OK, no problem.

06:55.760 --> 06:58.400
Helen, will you have someone
   clean up the graffiti

06:58.400 --> 06:59.920
in the men's room right away?

06:59.920 --> 07:01.080
                       That bad, huh?

07:01.080 --> 07:04.560
I don't think Mrs Auschlander
will appreciate being phoned

07:04.560 --> 07:07.320
for a good time.

07:07.320 --> 07:08.920
                          Oh, Daniel?

07:08.920 --> 07:11.400
I tried putting a patient
on the CT scanner.

07:11.400 --> 07:13.400
They said you'd reserved the machine.

07:13.400 --> 07:14.520
You look tired.

07:14.520 --> 07:18.520
Yeah, well, the baby's been
sounding readily at 1am, 3am, 4:30...

07:18.960 --> 07:20.720
    What's going on with the scanner?

07:20.720 --> 07:24.680
Boston Museum is X-raying
one of its Egyptian mummies.

07:24.680 --> 07:27.880
The city offered use of the
CAT scanners of all its hospitals.

07:27.880 --> 07:31.520
The museum wants to examine
its entire collection of mummies,

07:31.520 --> 07:33.960
utilising the new technology.
It's our turn.

07:33.960 --> 07:36.760
And how long are these
grave-robbers gonna tie us up?

07:36.760 --> 07:39.840
I've given them short periods
of time over the next two days.

07:39.840 --> 07:41.760
You can get in there
this afternoon.

07:41.760 --> 07:44.240
Well, I'd better.
Hospitals are supposed to be

07:44.240 --> 07:47.880
        for the living, not the dead.

07:47.880 --> 07:49.000
            Hiya, Lucy.

07:49.000 --> 07:51.640
Bobby. Hey, thanks.

07:51.640 --> 07:54.840
Whatever you did to my engine
yesterday, it's running great.

07:54.840 --> 07:56.800
I blew the moisture
out of your coil.

07:56.800 --> 07:57.920
The car has one, too?

07:57.920 --> 07:58.960
                                 Mmm.

07:58.960 --> 08:01.960
If you're trying to cop
another feel, I'll just stand here

08:01.960 --> 08:04.040
instead of being chased around.

08:04.040 --> 08:07.080
Would it be a normal day if
I didn't come by for a Long John?

08:07.080 --> 08:09.720
Oh, by this point,
I'd probably feel slighted.

08:09.720 --> 08:12.240
How'd it go last night, the date?
You get lucky?

08:12.240 --> 08:14.520
He probably thought so.

08:14.520 --> 08:15.680
Hmm.

08:15.680 --> 08:17.560
Nothing for the history books, huh?

08:17.560 --> 08:20.840
