08:20.840 --> 08:24.560
I thought you were one of those women
who like to go for the distance.

08:24.560 --> 08:27.600
The first boyfriend was a harrier,
  quick as a bunny.

08:27.600 --> 08:28.680
Gonna give this guy the heave-ho?

08:28.680 --> 08:30.120
Gonna give this guy the heave-ho?
I wasn't planning on it,

08:30.120 --> 08:34.120
until he made the comment that
I might consider breast implants.

08:34.600 --> 08:35.919
Look fine to me.

08:35.919 --> 08:38.039
I guess he doesn't have
     your good taste.

08:38.039 --> 08:41.559
Well, if you want another
professional peak under the hood,

08:41.559 --> 08:43.280
   I'll be glad to size you up.

08:43.280 --> 08:47.280
Have to show me yours
first, Caldwell!

08:49.320 --> 08:51.920
You two are really disgusting.

08:51.920 --> 08:55.920
Helen, it's been a pleasure
ignoring each other.

08:55.920 --> 08:58.840
Let's keep it up.

08:58.840 --> 09:00.440
  How could Craig do this to me?

09:00.440 --> 09:02.240
Be glad you're still working here.

09:02.240 --> 09:04.480
I'd rather be transferred
to accounting.

09:04.480 --> 09:06.640
OBGYN's no picnic for me, either.

09:06.640 --> 09:09.360
This rotation went south
            when Roxanne did.

09:09.360 --> 09:11.600
You're lucky, you get along
with women.

09:11.600 --> 09:13.200
What are you so afraid of?

09:13.200 --> 09:15.600
Women find me rude,
vulgar, insensitive.

09:15.600 --> 09:18.800
They make me crazy. I've dreamed
of touching them all my life.

09:18.800 --> 09:22.680
They excite me. When I get excited,
I say stupid things.

09:22.680 --> 09:25.280
Because you love women,
they think you hate them?

09:25.280 --> 09:27.800
I'm the pig poster child.
How do you deal with it?

09:27.800 --> 09:29.600
Well, you treat them like people.

09:29.600 --> 09:33.600
Treat them like people, right.

09:33.680 --> 09:35.880
Molly...

09:35.880 --> 09:38.040
This is Dr Ehrlich.
I'm going off-shift.

09:38.040 --> 09:42.040
He'll be handling your delivery.

09:46.360 --> 09:47.880
      I can't do it. Did you see her?

09:47.880 --> 09:50.280
I can't be detached
around that woman's body.

09:50.280 --> 09:53.520
Man's body, fine. I see them
at the Y all the time. But...

09:53.520 --> 09:54.840
Victor, you're a doctor.

09:54.840 --> 09:58.000
Surgeon. Then we're talking,
anaesthetised, open wounds.

09:58.000 --> 10:00.760
But heaving breasts
and the uro-genital tract...

10:00.760 --> 10:02.360
          Conscious women terrify me!

10:02.360 --> 10:04.520
Molly is the only woman
on the ward so far.

10:04.520 --> 10:06.320
Her water broke an hour ago.

10:06.320 --> 10:08.680
Maybe she'll deliver
after your shift ends.

10:08.680 --> 10:09.520
   That's seven hours from now.

10:09.520 --> 10:11.320
   That's seven hours from now.
She's three centimetres dilated.

10:11.320 --> 10:13.440
All I've got to do
is avoid her till then?

10:13.440 --> 10:15.080
That's one way of looking at it.

10:15.080 --> 10:17.720
OK, great.
I'll just play hide and seek

10:17.720 --> 10:21.720
until I can figure a way out.

10:24.000 --> 10:26.800
Have supply bring down
all the shampoo they've got.

10:26.800 --> 10:29.720
At least we can give these people
a cure for lice.

10:29.720 --> 10:32.640
Wayne! Thank God.
We need you around here.

10:32.640 --> 10:36.600
Westphall assigned me to the morgue
for a couple of days.

10:36.600 --> 10:37.960
             What are you doing here?

10:37.960 --> 10:41.600
Lonely. It seems like when I work
up here in ER, everybody dies.

10:41.600 --> 10:45.160
Down there, no customers.  Thought
I'd see what the problem was.

10:45.160 --> 10:48.800
Well, we had a pretty big
car accident a little while back,

10:48.800 --> 10:52.640
but unfortunately,
I think they're all gonna make it.

10:52.640 --> 10:55.560
Wayne? Dudley Bowman, remember me?

10:55.560 --> 10:58.680
I helped you move into that
pasty guy's apartment last year?

10:58.680 --> 11:00.520
Ehrlich? Right!

11:00.520 --> 11:03.000
You were the only one
who could drive the truck.

11:03.000 --> 11:05.720
Slept at our place
            for four days. Straight.

11:05.720 --> 11:07.440
How you doing?

11:07.440 --> 11:09.160
Good. Tired.

11:09.160 --> 11:12.720
Nobody's getting any sleep with
the cops running around. You've got

11:12.720 --> 11:16.600
to keep moving constantly otherwise
you'll wind up in the City Shelter.

11:16.600 --> 11:18.320
Nobody wants to live with bums.

11:18.320 --> 11:19.840
Good point.

11:19.840 --> 11:22.320
(COUGHS)

11:22.320 --> 11:25.640
That hack sounds bad.

11:25.640 --> 11:29.360
Ran into a rotten stream. Seems like
all the butts I find are unfiltered.

11:29.360 --> 11:31.400
Anyone examine you?

11:31.400 --> 11:32.040
I've been waiting.

11:32.040 --> 11:33.440
I've been waiting.
Why don't I take a look?

11:33.440 --> 11:35.040
It's not worth it, Wayne.

11:35.040 --> 11:38.440
Well, I've nothing to do
            anyway. Follow me.

11:38.440 --> 11:42.040
In that case, how about
letting me buy you breakfast after?

11:42.040 --> 11:43.640
You got the money?

11:43.640 --> 11:47.640
No, it just seemed like
a polite thing to say.

11:57.880 --> 12:01.240
Morena, you can use the dishwasher.

12:01.240 --> 12:02.520
Dishwasher?

12:02.520 --> 12:05.880
Dishwasher.
